{"tid":1461142,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［十萬火急］真係想台灣人幫我地既同我入黎！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T13:04:45.000Z","uid":212388,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a6671abef73e37dddee73ded725b436d4ce15608","tid":1461142,"uid":212388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"琴日見到香港人致臺灣人之公開信，我想講，喺連登post係冇用架，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇台灣人會黎睇連登</span></span>，黎左都睇唔明！有手足轉貼左去台灣論壇，但冇人理佢，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個論壇係台灣流量係數一數二</span></span>，真係要台灣人見到，真係要佢地知道發生緊咩事就應該要去佢地會去既地方post野。<br />\n<br />\n我建議，以後有任何同台灣有關既文宣或資訊，都要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">同步post去Dcard</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得要用返書面語</span></span>。仲有，唔好以為個個台灣人都係企係我地呢邊，未醒覺既台豬先係多數。<br />\n<br />\n下面係香港人致臺灣人之公開信既Dcard link，<strong>各位手足唔好留言「推」或者「 Push」</strong>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要禁左下角粒心<br />\n要禁左下角粒心<br />\n要禁左下角粒心</span></span><br />\n咁樣先可以推到上熱門比更多台灣人（台豬）見到！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/trending/p/231841775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Ftrending%2Fp%2F231841775&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=32e48162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/trending/p/231841775</a>"},{"pid":"fac14af59e96d2be3a9fd6d14bc1fb9925dd1723","tid":1461142,"uid":212388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"改左名 唔好屌我P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ff908d297f9868a54dbae39642a758353dc09e","tid":1461142,"uid":212388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b4d5b6081f924f3b692662d755e8e2a179de423a","tid":1461142,"uid":212388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019